name: Chicken & Couscous Fusion Bowl 1
ingredients: couscous, chicken, zucchini, broccoli, turmeric, avocado
steps: 1. Cook the couscous until tender. 2. Sauté the chicken with turmeric. 3. Add chopped zucchini and broccoli, cook until soft. 4. Stir in avocado, mix well. 5. Serve hot, optionally garnished with herbs or seeds.

steps: 1. Prepare the poha by boiling or soaking. 2. Cook the lentils separately with spices. 3. Mix carrot, cauliflower, green chili and sauté for a few minutes. 4. Combine everything, add lemon juice, and simmer for 5 minutes. 5. Serve hot with garnish if desired.
